retaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Aprajita%20Singh%2C%20assisting%20the%20court%20as%20amicus%20curiae%2C%20said%20if%20their%20law%20was%20being%20violated%2C%20they%20have%20the%20authority%20to%20take%20action.%20%26quot%3BBut%20they%20are%20being%20silent%20spectators%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Singh%20said%20thousands%20of%20crores%20were%20offered%20to%20the%20farmers%20for%20equipment%20to%20help%20stop%20stubble%20burning.%20%26quot%3BIn%202017%2C%20we%20thought%20it%20would%20help%20stop%2C%20but%20it%20has%20not%20and%20that%20is%20why%20the%20CAQM%20has%20come%20today%20and%20now%20some%20officer%20has%20to%20be%20held%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20efforts%20must%20be%20taken%20to%20ensure%20the%20use%20of%20stubble-burning%20alternatives%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOne%20of%20the%20duties%20is%20to%20work%20with%20NCR%20States%20and%20it%20(CAQM)%20has%20vast%20powers%20conferred%20including%20closure%20of%20polluting%20units.%20We%20are%20of%20the%20view%20that%20though%20the%20Commission%20has%20taken%20certain%20steps%2C%20the%20Commission%20needs%20to%20be%20more%20active%20and%20must%20ensure%20that%20its%20efforts%20and%20directions%20actually%20translate%20into%20reducing%20the%20problem%20of%20pollution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20asked%20the%20CAQM%20to%20submit%20the%20details%20of%20their%20meetings%20and%20a%20better%20compliance%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20matter%20will%20be%20heard%20again%20next%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727433300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2F29gj1jdo_delhi-pollution-afp_625x300_18_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fall-in-the-air-supreme-court-comes-down-heavily-on-delhi-air-quality-panel-6661776%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20C