2C%20and%2014.%20They%20know%20I%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20leave%20them%20a%20substantial%20inheritance.%20Here's%20what%20I'm%20doing%20instead%2C%20and%20how%20I%20talk%20with%20them%20about%20money%20and%20wealth.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22George%20Appling%20dressed%20up%20at%20the%20medieval%20fair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66eaea60d17aa3c7b2b3b185%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGeorge%20Appling%20at%20the%20Sherwood%20Forest%20Faire%20in%202023.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20George%20Appling%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a3c71dda-254c-4a09-b734-e07f90c5a1a4%5C%22%3EI%20believe%20it's%20bad%20to%20make%20your%20kids%20wealthy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20want%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleave-money-will-child-who-doesnt-like-me-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20my%20children%20money%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20I%20believe%20it's%20bad%20to%20make%20your%20children%20wealthy.%20If%20money%20comes%20too%20easily%2C%20it%20has%20a%20very%20good%20chance%20of%20ruining%20your%20ambition.%20I%20want%20my%20children%20to%20have%20the%20motivation%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20went%20to%20Harvard%20Business%20School%20and%20attended%20a%20reunion%20about%20a%20decade%20ago.%20There%2C%20I%20attended%20a%20lecture%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbiracial-didnt-understand-generational-wealth-growing-up-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egenerational%20wealth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20professor%20asked%20who%20had%20heard%20the%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20takes%20one%20generation%20to%20build%20it%2C%20one%20generation%20to%20run%20it%2C%20and%20one%20generation%20to%20ruin%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20common%20refrain%20about%20wealth.%20He%20then%20showed%20us%20the%20same%20saying%20in%20dozens%20of%20languages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20cultures%20all%20over%20the%20globe%20share%20this%20warning%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20generational%20wealth%2C%20I%20think%20it's%20worth%20heralding.%20I'm%20also%20a%20history%20buff%2C%20and%20believe%20history%20shows%20that%20leaving%20tremendous%20wealth%20is%20harmful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c32a6694-c9e3-48f8-8799-2eea1056eff0%5C%22%3EI'll%20pay%20for%20a%20car%2C%20college%2C%20and%20first%20down%20payment%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20kids%20know%20that%20I'll%20pay%20for%20their%20college%20(up%20to%20about%20%24100%2C000%20each)%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Ftips-for-saving-for-a-down-payment%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%20on%20their%20first%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20their%20first%20car.%20All%20of%20these%20amounts%20need%20to%20be%20reasonable%20and%20practical%2C%20not%20flashy%20or%20to%20show%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20turned%2016%20in%20April%2C%20so%20Brian%20and%20I%20took%20her%20car%20shopping.%20We%20set%20a%20budget%20of%20%2425%2C000.%20She%20bought%20a%20nine-year-old%20Nissan%20Pathfinder%20for%20%2423%2C000.%20The%20car%20was%20top-of-the-line%20when%20it%20was%20made%2C%20so%20it%20has%20some%20nice%20bells%20and%20whistles%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20very%20practical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6e96e08-3e33-41be-b687-f9a3079c6eb3%5C%22%3EI'll%20establish%20a%20trust%20to%20make%20business%20loans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20established%20a%20trust%20that%20will%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-of-five-cant-afford-paying-college-kids-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epay%20for%20college%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20car%2C%20and%20a%20down%20payment%20for%20my%20descendants%20in%20future%20generations.%20The%20trust%2C%20which%20I%20based%20on%20the%20Rockefeller%20family%20trust%2C%20will%20also%20make%20business%20loans%20to%20my%20descendants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20get%20a%20loan%2C%20they%20must%20present%20a%20business%20plan%20that's%20evaluated%20by%20a%20third%20party.%20Each%20descendent%20will%20only%20get%20one%20loan%20in%20their%20lifetime%2C%20unless%20they%20pay%20the%20loan%20back%20in%20full.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220ed3ba1e-48bd-496a-95b5-e6c36442cdaa%5C%22%3EMy%20kids%20get%20a%20%2425%20weekly%20allowance%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20of%20my%20kids%20gets%20an%20allowance%20of%20%2425%20a%20week%20if%20they%20do%20basic%20chores%2C%20like%20cleaning%20up%20after%20dinner%20and%20emptying%20the%20trash.%20The%20allowance%20covers%20wants%20%E2%80%94%20like%20Starbucks%2C%20which%20they%20all%20love.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrian%20and%20I%20pay%20for%20all%20needs.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20lines%20between%20wants%20and%20needs%20aren't%20hard%20and%20fast.%20If%20the%20kids%20need%20%2420%20to%20go%20to%20the%20trampoline%20park%20with%20friends%2C%20I'll%20usually%20pay.%20If%20they%20need%20sunglasses%2C%20I'm%20happy%20to%20buy%20them%20a%20%2425%20pair%2C%20but%20if%20they%20want%20%24200%20brand-name%20sunglasses%2C%20they're%20on%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d2c6685-db9b-41c3-a450-e2fade070da9%5C%22%3EI%20demonstrate%20living%20below%20my%20means%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20important%20habits%20a%20human%20can%20make%20is%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-money-advice-no-one-wants-to-hear-spend-less-than-earned-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espend%20less%20than%20you%20earn%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There's%20a%20huge%20comfort%20in%20having%20money%20in%20the%20bank.%20Living%20below%20my%20means%20helped%20me%20build%20financial%20security%20that%20let%20me%20start%20a%20family%2C%20so%20I%20demonstrate%20it%20for%20my%20kids.%20For%20example%2C%20I%20drive%20a%202016%20Ford%20F250.%20It's%20not%20flashy%2C%20but%20it's%20practical%20for%20hauling%20horses%20and%20hay%2C%20so%20