20they%20wrote%20in%20the%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20Dell%20told%20workers%20who%20opted%20in%20for%20hybrid%20work%20that%20three%20days%20on-site%20a%20week%20was%20sufficient.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20also%20began%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-hybrid-return-to-office-mandate-monitor-employees-onsite-attendance-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonitoring%20their%20attendance%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20tracking%20badge%20swipes%20and%20categorizing%20workers%20with%20color-coded%20flags.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20workers%20told%20BI%20that%20Dell's%20vision%20of%20in-office%20work%20wasn't%20panning%20out%20as%20planned.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdell-remote-workers-promotion-return-office-push-flexible-work-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOver%20half%20the%20company%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20opted%20to%20stay%20remote%2C%20meaning%20many%20offices%20were%20empty.%20Others%20had%20multiple%20team%20members%20in%20different%20time%20zones%2C%20so%20were%20still%20communicating%20over%20Zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20the%20same%20thing%20that%20I%20would%20at%20home%2C%20talk%20to%20the%20same%20people%20who%20are%20in%20a%20different%20office%2C%20and%20then%20I%20spend%20an%20hour%20in%20traffic%20coming%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20employee%20in%20the%20sales%20division%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScannell%20and%20Byrne%20said%20this%20week's%20move%20would%20help%20it%20to%20harness%20an%20environment%20of%20%26quot%3Bhigh%20energy%26quot%3B%20and%20help%20staffers%20to%20grow%20their%20skills.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20also%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20enter%20a%20new%20AI%20world%2C%20in-person%20human%20interaction%20will%20be%20more%20important%20than%20ever.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20policy%20follows%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fread-memo-dell-staff-restructuring-layoffs-jobs-ai-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20major%20restructuring%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20sales%20division%20announced%20in%20August%20as%20part%20of%20what%20leaders%20termed%20its%20%26quot%3Bmodernization%20journey.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20streamlined%20sales%20teams%2C%20introduced%20new%20AI-enabled%20processes%2C%20and%20carried%20out%20some%20of%20the%20largest%20layoffs%20in%20the%20company's%20recent%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Vivek%20Mohindra%2C%20SVP%20of%20Corporate%20Strategy%20at%20Dell%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20hybrid%20approach%20was%20%26quot%3Ban%20important%20way%20of%20working.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hybrid%20approach%20allows%20us%20to%20not%20only%20be%20able%20to%20bring%20people%20in%20the%20room%20and%20have%20those%20conversations%20and%20move%20much%20faster%2C%20but%20also%20at%20the%20right%20times%2C%20be%20able%20to%20use%20the%20remote%20aspects%20of%20their%20work%20to%20be%20able%20to%20execute%20those%2C%26quot%3B%20Mohindra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20policy%20%3Cspan%3Efollows%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-return-to-office-mandate-5-days-week-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAmazon's%20announcement%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20it%20will%20end%20its%20remote%20working%20arrangements%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20with%20CEO%20Andy%20Jassy%20telling%3C%2Fspan%3E%20employees%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week%20from%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDell%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%2C%20made%20outside%20normal%20working%20hours.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ERead%20the%20full%20memo%20below%3A%20%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EHi%20Team%2C%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20sales%20force%20has%20a%20culture%20of%20winning%20and%20a%20reputation%20of%20outpacing%20the%20competition.%20We%20are%20the%20best%20in%20the%20business!%20That%20