edly%20preparing%20to%20become%20a%20for-profit%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20move%20that%20could%20see%20the%20OpenAI%20chief%20gain%20more%20decision-making%20power%2C%20a%20legal%20expert%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20is%20considering%20a%20change%20under%20which%20it%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20governed%20by%20its%20nonprofit%20board%2C%20Reuters%20and%20Bloomberg%20reported%20Thursday%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmira-murati-openai-cto-leaving-executive-memo-staff-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esudden%20exit%20of%20the%20company's%20chief%20technology%20officer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Mira%20Murati%2C%20triggered%20a%20wave%20of%20speculation%20about%20the%20company's%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reports%20have%20come%20more%20than%20a%20year%20after%20Altman%20said%20OpenAI's%20structure%20was%20atypical%20but%20a%20deliberate%20setup%20because%20%26quot%3BAI%20is%20an%20unusual%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloomberg%20reported%20that%20Altman%20was%20also%20in%20discussions%20to%20receive%20a%207%25%20equity%20stake%20in%20OpenAI%2C%20a%20move%20that%20would%20mark%20his%20first%20ownership%20claim%20in%20the%20company.%20At%20an%20OpenAI%20all-hands%20on%20Thursday%2C%20however%2C%20Altman%20denied%20that%20there%20were%20plans%20for%20him%20to%20receive%20a%20%26quot%3Bgiant%20equity%20stake%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20company%2C%20according%20to%20CNBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20could%20be%20structured%20as%20a%20public-benefit%20corporation%2C%20Bloomberg%20reported%2C%20an%20entity%20that%20balances%20profit%20with%20mission.%20It's%20a%20structure%20resembling%20that%20of%20Open%20AI's%20rivals%20Anthropic%20and%20xAI%2C%20Elon%20Musk's%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20OpenAI%20spokesperson%20told%20the%20outlet%20the%20nonprofit%20entity%20%26quot%3Bwill%20continue%20to%20exist%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20core%20to%20its%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20was%20established%20as%20a%20nonprofit%20in%202015%2C%20but%20in%202019%2C%20it%20created%20a%20%26quot%3Bcapped%20profit%26quot%3B%20subsidiary%2C%20OpenAI%20LP.%20This%20allowed%20it%20to%20accept%20a%20cumulative%20investment%20of%20more%20than%20%2413%20billion%20from%20Microsoft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERestructuring%20to%20a%20public-benefit%20corporation%20would%20probably%20make%20OpenAI%20more%20attractive%20to%20further%20investment%20at%20a%20time%20when%20it's%20reported%20to%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopenai-fundraising-150-billion-valuation-new-funding-round-altman-thrive-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraising%20money%20at%20a%20%24150%20billion%20valuation%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Altman%20would%20stand%20to%20get%20as%20much%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fopen-ai-sam-altman-equity-stake-valuation-private-nonprofit-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2410.5%20billion%20richer%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20rumored%20equity%20stake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223abd25e1-cbdf-4850-b634-16bcc3a650f3%5C%22%3EAltman%20could%20have%20more%20decision-making%20power%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20for-profit%20structure%20could%20be%20%26quot%3Bbetter%20for%20Altman%26quot%3B%20in%20other%20ways%2C%20Anat%20Alon-Beck%2C%20a%20researcher%20focused%20on%20corporate%20law%20and%20governance%20at%20Case%20Western%20Reserve%20University's%20School%20of%20Law%2C%20told%20BI.%20It%20could%20give%20%26quot%3Bmore%20power%20to%20shareholders%20over%20decision-making%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20especially%20if%20they're%20a%20controlling%20shareholder%2C%20which%20Altman%20could%20become.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlon-Beck%20said%20the%20new%20entity's%20shareholders%20would%20need%20to%20elect%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20members%20at%20an%20annual%20meeting%2C%20and%20the%20directors%20would%20then%20be%20responsible%20for%20the%20company's%20policy%20and%20direction%20and%20for%20hiring%20the%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20public-benefit%20corporations%20and%20nonprofits%20share%20commitments%20to%20social%20or%20environmental%20goals%2C%20Alon-Beck%20said%20their%20structures%20and%20purposes%20differ.%20Chief%20among%20those%20differences%20is%20that%20the%20new%20entity%20would%20be%20owned%20by%20shareholders%20who%20expect%20the%20company%20to%20make%20a%20profit%20and%20return%20some%20of%20that%20money%20to%20them%20as%20dividends%2C%20she%20said.%20Unlike%20OpenAI's%20previous%20arrangement%2C%20there%20would%20be%20no%20cap%20on%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b4065f4-0d9a-4b3d-9a4e-175f83c56f99%5C%22%3EOpenAI%20would%20no%20longer%20enjoy%20nonprofit%20tax%20benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20which%20is%20registered%20in%20Delaware%2C%20may%20see%20its%20tax%20status%20change.%20Delaware%20public-benefit%20corporations%20must%20submit%20a%20report%20to%20shareholders%20every%20two%20years%2C%20laying%20out%20how%20much%20progress%20they've%20made%20toward%20their%20goal%20of%20positively%20impacting%20society.%20Like%20any%20other%20US%20company%2C%20benefit%20corporations%20must%20pay%20taxes%20on%20their%20profits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20emphasis%20will%20now%20be%20on%20making%20a%20profit%2C%20and%20any%20tax%20benefits%20that%20it%20enjoyed%20as%20a%20result%20of%20its%20nonprofit%20status%20will%20go%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20Eric%20Chaffee%2C%20a%20professor%20of%20business%20law%20at%20Case%20Western%20Reserve%20University%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChaffee%20said%20for-profit%20benefit%20corporations%20were%20a%20relatively%20new%20business%20entity%2C%20and%20the%20law%20surrounding%20them%20was%20still%20evolving.%20In%20his%20view%2C%20the%20potential%20restructuring%20is%20happening%20partly%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20investors%20to%20cash%20out%20and%20see%20large%20returns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%