20discussions%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20Israelis%20about%20the%20ceasefire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20clear%20to%20us%20that%20from%20a%20practical%20perspective%2C%20that%20there%20isn't%20cause%20for%20us%20to%20continue%20to%20have%20these%20conversations%20with%20the%20Israelis%2C%26quot%3B%20Kirby%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20contradictory%20messaging%20-%20the%20US%20insisting%20Israel%20is%20considering%20its%20proposal%2C%20and%20Israel%20insisting%20it's%20not%20-%20further%20perpetuated%20a%20trend%20that's%20come%20to%20define%20the%20conflict%20and%20raised%20fresh%20questions%20about%20the%20US%20strategy%20to%20try%20to%20end%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20rejection%20bore%20strong%20echoes%20of%20a%20dialog%20that%20revolved%20around%20the%20bid%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20to%20halt%20the%20fighting%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20nearly%20a%20year%20after%20the%20militant%20group's%20Oct.%207%20attack.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeatedly%2C%20the%20US%20has%20said%20Israel%20was%20onboard%20with%20its%20plan%20and%20an%20accord%20was%20close%2C%20only%20for%20Netanyahu%20and%20his%20government%20to%20say%20they%20don't%20see%20a%20ceasefire%20coming%20anytime%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%2C%20analysts%20and%20government%20officials%20argue%20that%20for%20whatever%20the%20flaws%20of%20the%20strategy%2C%20the%20Biden%20administration%20has%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20continue.%20They%20suggested%20that%20the%20three-week%20ceasefire%20plan%20for%20Lebanon%2C%20with%20its%20dozen%20signatories%20along%20with%20the%20EU%2C%20may%20have%20been%20meant%20as%20a%20signal%20to%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20see%20this%20as%20critical%20US%20leadership%20maximally%20leveraging%20diplomatic%20alliances%20to%20sharpen%20Israeli%20understanding%20and%20appreciation%20of%20the%20costs%20of%20proceeding%20unilaterally%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mara%20Rudman%2C%20who%20worked%20on%20Middle%20East%20issues%20during%20the%20Clinton%20and%20Obama%20administrations.%20%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20heard%20and%20perhaps%20needs%20to%20sink%20in.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20unveiling%20the%20ceasefire%2C%20the%20US%2C%20France%20and%20others%20marshaled%20a%20broad%20coalition%20to%20try%20and%20push%20the%20process%20forward.%20But%20now%20both%20US%20and%20French%20officials%20appear%20to%20be%20effectively%20ignoring%20Netanyahu's%20rejection%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20he%20will%20come%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20Ottawa%20on%20Thursday%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20said%20Netanyahu%20would%20be%20making%20a%20mistake%20by%20rejecting%20the%20Lebanon%20plan%20because%20it%20would%20make%20him%20responsible%20for%20%26quot%3Ban%20escalation%20far%20beyond%20that%20which%20no%20one%20would%20be%20able%20to%20control.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20doesn't%20account%20for%20the%20pressure%20Netanyahu%20is%20coming%20under%20at%20home.%20Tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20Israelis%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20areas%20near%20the%20Lebanese%20border%20and%20are%20clamoring%20to%20return.%20But%20even%20Israel%20appeared%20to%20acknowledge%20it%20had%20overstepped.%20Later%20Thursday%2C%20Netanyahu's%20office%20expressed%20appreciation%20for%20the%20Biden%20administration's%20efforts%20and%20%26quot%3Bindispensable%26quot%3B%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20acknowledged%20that%20the%20US%20was%20seeking%20to%20promote%20a%20ceasefire%2C%20but%20stopped%20short%20of%20endorsing%20this%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20diplomats%20familiar%20with%20the%20Biden%20administration%20approach%20said%20the%20impression%20other%20nations%20get%20is%20that%20the%20US%20has%20been%20repeatedly%20embarrassed%20by%20Israel.%20The%20diplomats%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20discussing%20private%20assessments%2C%20said%20the%20US%20sacrificed%20its%20own%20standing%20when%20an%20ally%20such%20as%20Israel%20so%20blatantly%20flouts%20its%20wishes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impatience%20with%20Biden's%20approach%20may%20be%20growing.%20On%20Thursday%2C%20Senator%20Tim%20Kaine%2C%20a%20Virginia%20Democrat%2C%20said%20he%20would%20vote%20to%20oppose%20offensive%20weapons%20to%20Israel.%20He%20called%20them%20%26quot%3Ban%20accelerant%20to%20ongoing%20hostilities.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20had%20to%20walk%20a%20fine%20line%20between%20likely%20Democratic%20voters%20with%20sympathies%20on%20either%20side%20of%20the%20conflict%2C%20particularly%20given%20the%20razor-thin%20margins%20in%20swing%20states%20expected%20to%20decide%20the%20presidential%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20seems%20to%20believe%20that%20%26quot%3Bmerely%20expressing%20the%20expectation%20that%20a%20deal%20is%20imminent%20or%20within%20reach%20-%20that%20this%20will%20put%20pressure%20on%20Netanyahu%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Khaled%20Elgindy%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%20Institute.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20they're%20trying%20to%20manifest%20a%20ceasefire%20into%20being%20without%20actually%20applying%20real%20pressure%20or%20using%20any%20of%20the%20vast%20leverage%20at%20their%20disposal.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727421360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fuj62iglo_lebanon-_625x300_27_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Flebanon-ceasefire-confusion-tests-us-approach-to-israel-again-6660893%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20shared%20a%20brief%20moment%20of%20optimism%20on%20Wednesday%20as%20they%20unveiled%20a%20three-week%20ceasefire%20proposal%20to%20halt%20the%20violence%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hezbollah.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%2