ise%20on%20a%20range%20of%20different%20topics%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-6-1726748092.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-6-1726748092-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-6-1726748092-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-6-1726748092-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-6-1726748092-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366766%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIF.BE%20is%20a%20space%20where%20artists%20can%20converge%20and%20discuss%20ideas%20as%20well%20as%20come%20together%20to%20share%20their%20expertise%20on%20a%20range%20of%20different%20topics%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20being%20said%2C%20care%20was%20taken%20to%20not%20use%20any%20cement%20in%20the%20restoration%20process.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20discovered%20that%20the%20brickwork%20that%20lay%20under%20the%20plaster%20was%20a%20composite%20brick%20and%20wood%20combination.%20This%20gave%20stability%20to%20the%20walls.%20It%20also%20took%20care%20of%20the%20seismic%20aspects.%20We%20restored%20the%20wood%20and%20the%20brick.%20The%20only%20new%20material%20that%20we%20bought%20on%20site%20was%20a%20very%20small%20quantity%20of%20lightweight%20steel%2C%20which%20was%20used%20to%20cover%20the%20courtyard%20space%20and%20for%20the%20galvanised%20iron%20roofs.%E2%80%9D%20It%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20the%20building%E2%80%99s%20past%20gave%20way%20to%20its%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20IF.BE%20is%20an%20architecturally%20striking%20oasis%20of%20sustainability%20with%20detail%20in%20each%20corner.%20But%2C