2%80%98How%20do%20I%20know%20if%20she%E2%80%99s%20getting%20enough%20milk%3F%E2%80%99%20kept%20worrying%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gayathri%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20experienced%20a%20complete%20breakdown%20when%20her%20daughter%20was%20three%20weeks%20old.%20%E2%80%9CAround%20that%20time%2C%20she%20was%20cluster%20feeding.%20Even%20right%20after%20feeding%2C%20she%20would%20cry%20as%20if%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20received%20any%20milk.%20This%20continued%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20People%2C%20including%20my%20own%20mom%2C%20said%20she%20was%20being%20fussy%20as%20my%20milk%20supply%20was%20not%20enough.%20This%20deeply%20affected%20my%20confidence.%20I%20felt%20shattered%20and%20as%20if%20I%20was%20starving%20my%20own%20baby%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20everyone%20celebrates%20pregnancy%2C%20Gayathri%20notes%20that%20not%20many%20offer%20support%20to%20women%20during%20their%20most%20difficult%20postpartum%20periods.%20%E2%80%9CA%20woman%20going%20through%20a%20cocktail%20of%20emotions%20is%20blamed%20for%20not%20producing%20enough%20milk%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20month%20with%20her%20daughter%2C%20Gayathri%E2%80%99s%20anxiousness%20turned%20into%20guilt.%20She%20reached%20out%20to%20her%20friends%20and%20cousins%2C%20but%20they%20advised%20her%20to%20consider%20formula%20feeding.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20determined%20to%20breastfeed%20my%20child%20as%20breastfed%20babies%20have%20a%20lower%20risk%20of%20developing%20many%20diseases%20like%20asthma%2C%20obesity%2C%20ear%20infections%2C%20and%20more%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnaricare-3-1727337840.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202022%2C%20Gayathri%20launched%20her%20startup%20NariCare%20to%20revolut