0s%2C%20Kolar%2C%20Karnataka%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20brothers%2C%20Manjunath%20and%20Raghavendra%20Shanmugam%2C%20were%20returning%20from%20school.%20As%20they%20chatted%2C%20Manjunath%20told%20his%20younger%20brother%20how%20he%20had%20stopped%20a%20classmate%20from%20bullying%20another%20student.%20This%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20this%20young%20boy%20had%20dared%20to%20question%20what%20was%20clearly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENovember%202005%2C%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20same%20righteous%20boy%20was%20now%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F307264%2Fgps-renewables-mainak-chakraborty-sreekrishna-sankar-ev-charging-station-biogas-to-electricity%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIM%20graduate%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20and%20a%20sales%20officer%20at%20the%20Indian%20Oil%20Corporation%20(IOC).%20One%20of%20his%20responsibilities%20was%20checking%20petrol%20adulteration%20at%20petrol%20pumps.%20He%20set%20out%20on%20a%20tour%20of%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20district%20in%20November%202005.%20He%20found%20anomalies%2C%20for%20the%20second%20time%2C%20at%20the%20Mittal%20Automobile%20Petrol%20Pump%20and%20was%20about%20to%20take%20measures%20to%20seal%20it.%20On%20the%20night%20of%2019%20November%2C%20he%20was%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20family%2C%20who%20were%20attending%20a%20family%20function%20in%20Chennai%2C%20were%20shocked%20beyond%20words.%20How%20could%20they%20even%20begin%20to%20fathom%20such%20an%20unjust%20shooting%20%E2%80%94%20where%20their%20son%E2%80%99s%20life%20was%20cut%20short%20for%20simply%20standing%20up%20for%20what%20was%20right%3F%20As%20they%20grappled%20with%20the%20loss%20of%20their%2027-year-old%20son%2C%20the%20news%20sent%20shockwaves%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20hundred%20kilometres%20away%2C%20in%20Mysuru%2C%20a%20young%20couple%2C%20Anjali%20Mullatti%20and%20H%20Jaishankar%2C%20watched%20the%20news%20unfold%20on%20their%20TV%20screens.%20As%20IIM%20alumni%20themselves%2C%20they%20were%20shocked.%20There%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20anger%2C%20grief%2C%20and%20frustration%20within%20the%20IIM%20alumni%20groups%20across%20Ahmedabad%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Calcutta%2C%20and%20Lucknow%20%E2%80%94%20the%20four%20IIMs%20at%20that%20time.%20While%20many%20vented%20their%20grief%20and%20anger%2C%20no%20one%20seemed%20to%20be%20doing%20anything%20on%20the%20ground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20decided%20they%20would%20take%20action%20if%20no%20one%20else%20did.%20Their%20efforts%20led%20them%20to%20Kamini%20Jaiswal%2C%20a%20prominent%20Supreme%20Court%20lawyer%2C%20who%20connected%20them%20with%20criminal%20lawyer%20I%20B%20Singh%20in%20Lucknow.%20Thus%20began%20their%20fight%20to%20get%20justice%20for%20Manjunath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20took%20turns%20going%20to%20Lakhimpur%20Kheri%20for%20every%20hearing%2C%20pushing%20for%20a%20fast-track%20trial%20that%20led%20to%20a%20verdict%20within%2010%20months.%20All%20the%20eight%20accused%20were%20found%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20forever%20indebted%20to%20them.%20They%20ensured%20justice%20for%20my%20brother.%20Though%20we%20can%20never%20get%20him%20back%2C%20we%20found%20some%20peace%20after%20the%20convicts%20were%20sentenced%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Raghavendra.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENo%20longer%20mute%20spectators%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20recall%20watching%20the%20news%20about%20Manjunath%20as%20if%20it%20were%20yesterday.%20On%20one%20hand%2C%20there%20was%20anger%20toward%20IOC%20for%20allowing%20this%20to%20happen%2C%20while%20on%20the%20other%2C%20seeing%20his%20grieving%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20simple%2C%20middle-class%20folks%20%E2%80%94%20grapple%20with%20the%20magnitude%20of%20this%20irreparable%20loss%20was%20heart-wrenching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20196px)%20100vw%2C%20196px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-1726828841.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22196%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manjunath%20with%20his%20friend%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-1726828841.jpeg%20196w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fmanjunath-1726828841-150x230.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366859%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EManjunath%20with%20his%20friend%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EManjunath%E2%80%99s%20mother%20made%20a%20statement%20on%20TV%20that%20echoed%20across%20the%20country%3A%20%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20crying%20tears%20of%20blood.%20What%20can%20we%20(husband%20and%20wife)%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20helplessness%20of%20the%20common%20people%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20harsh%20system%20was%20painfully%20evident.%20Anjali%20and%20Jaishankar%20were%20unable%20to%20forget%20Manjunath%20or%20what%20his%20mother%20had%20said.%20It%20was%20time%20for%20action.%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20his%20parents%20may%20not%20have%20been%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F331304%2Fdevanshi-yadav-shaheed-ramashray-welfare-society-bareilly-acid-attack-sexual-abuse-survivor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efight%20against%20the%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%2C%20as%20a%20community%20